  <summary>11/19/1999--Introduced.
Prohibits the deduction under the Internal Revenue Code of any payment under a foreign-based Holocaust victims' settlement if no deduction would be allowed under the Code for such payment were it made directly by the foreign bank or other entity entering into such settlement.</summary>
